column5: Planning on going to Puslinch on Saturday, just wondering knows how thick the ice is.... Also how people are making out on Puslinch if they have been ice fishing it this year!  Thanks Luc
I take it that theirs no ice
Last I checked it was wide open, if there is ice it wont be safe
Alright thanks! Do you know anything about Guelph Lake?
There's no trespassing no access signs all over the restaurant parking lot, so even if there is ice you need another access point.
